---
---
<section class="page-container section-spacer">
  <div class="glow-line-magenta"></div>
  <p class="eyebrow fade-in" style="color: var(--color-magenta);">interface</p>
  <h2 class="fade-in-up delay-1" style="max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);">Designed for clarity.</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-2">
      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: var(--color-bg-elevated); aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden;">
          <img src="/screenshots/today@2x.svg" alt="Today" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono);">Today</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Timeline, tasks, habits, events, all visible at a glance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-3">
      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: var(--color-bg-elevated); aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden;">
          <img src="/screenshots/calendar@2x.svg" alt="Calendar" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono);">Calendar</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Month view with habit events and color-coded categories.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-4">
      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: var(--color-bg-elevated); aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden;">
          <img src="/screenshots/chat@2x.svg" alt="AI assistant" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono);">AI assistant</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Streaming responses with visible tool calls and confirmation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-5">
      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: var(--color-bg-elevated); aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden;">
          <img src="/screenshots/insights@2x.svg" alt="Insights" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono);">Insights</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Mood trends, correlations, heatmaps, weekly reflection.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-6">
      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: var(--color-bg-elevated); aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden;">
          <img src="/screenshots/notes@2x.svg" alt="Notes" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono);">Notes</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Two-pane layout with searchable sidebar and full-text editor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-7">
      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: var(--color-bg-elevated); aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden;">
          <img src="/screenshots/settings@2x.svg" alt="Settings" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-mono);">Settings</h4>
      <p class="body-small">LLM provider, Telegram pairing, notifications, data export.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
